         <t:abstract>
            <t:p><t:persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS3082Chaine">Marius Chaîne</t:persName> mistakenly identified this malkǝʾ-hymn as the one for
               <t:persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS9848Walatta">Walatta Ṗeṭros</t:persName> in 
               <t:bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/7WA33SUX"><seg type="journalArticle"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Chaine1913Rep"/><title level="a">Répertoire des Salam et Malkeʾe contenus dans les manuscrits éthiopiens des bibliothèques d’Europe</title><title level="j">Revue de l’Orient Chrétien</title><author><t:forename>Marius</t:forename><t:surname>Chaîne</t:surname></author><date>1913</date><biblScope unit="volume">18</biblScope><biblScope unit="issue">2 and 4 (Deuxième série, 8/2 and 8/4)</biblScope><biblScope unit="page">183–203 and 337–357</biblScope><note type="url">http://catholicapedia.net/Documents/Revue-de-l.Orient-chretien/18-1913_revue-de-l.orient-ch_paris.pdf</note></t:bibl>, but the tarafa malkǝʾ is dedicated to 
               <t:persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS3698ehetaKr">ʾƎḫǝta Krǝstos</t:persName> and follows upon malkǝʾ <t:ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2892RepCh173"><span xmlns="" class="w3-tag w3-red">No item: LIT2892RepCh173</span></t:ref>
            </t:p>
         </t:abstract>
